## Project Structure

```
zsom/
├── zsom/                  # Core package
│   ├── __init__.py        # Public API + CLI entry point
│   ├── __main__.py        # python -m zsom support
│   ├── som.py             # SOM class + hex grid + PCA init
│   ├── metrics.py         # Distance functions
│   ├── datasets.py        # Data generators
│   ├── error_metrics.py   # qE, MAE, MSE, RMSE, MAPE
│   ├── numba_accel.py     # Optional JIT kernels
│   └── visualization.py   # Plotting + animation
├── examples/              # Ready-to-run demos
│   ├── demo_clusters.py
│   ├── demo_bunny.py
│   ├── demo_all.py
│   └── notebook.ipynb
├── som.py                 # Backward-compat shim
├── pyproject.toml         # PEP 621 metadata
├── setup.py               # pip install -e . shim
├── setup.cfg              # setuptools config
└── README.md
```

